                    </p>
                    <p>
        Comfort and elegance in every room
    </p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-6 col-lg-3">
                    <p class="h1-fs">02</p>
                    <p>
                      <img src="/web/image/hotel.s_key_images_default_image_2" class="img img-fluid rounded" alt="" style="width: 100% !important;" loading="lazy"/>
                    </p>
                    <p>
        A perfect getaway for families and couples alike
    </p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-6 col-lg-3">
                    <p class="h1-fs">03</p>
                    <p>
                      <img src="/web/image/hotel.s_key_images_default_image_3" class="img img-fluid rounded" alt="" style="width: 100% !important;" loading="lazy"/>
                    </p>
                    <p>
        Relaxing spaces that cater to your every need
    </p>
